boilerplate.containers.Topic.test.title: Serbian water polo players attacked in Split
boilerplate.containers.Topic.test.descri: "We strongly condemn the attack on Red Star athletes, there is absolutely no justification for violence. We pride ourselves on being a city of sport, tourism and hospitality! Such nationalist outbursts are just throwing a ball on our city. A man can not choose whether to be born as a Serb or a Croat, but he can choose whether he will be a man or not", said the young SDP
